-- Raya Is in Talks With NBE on $30 Million Loan, Al Mal Reports
-- B y   A h m e d   A .   N a m a t a l l a
-- 2012-07-12T09:18:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-12/raya-is-in-talks-with-nbe-on-30-million-loan-al-mal-reports.html
Raya Holding Co., an Egyptian
information technology company, is in talks with National Bank
of Egypt about a loan of 183 million Egyptian pounds ($30
million),  Al Mal  reported, citing Sherif Riad, NBE’s head of
corporate banking.  The seven-year loan would help to finance Raya’s 311
million-pound administrative building, which is under
construction on the outskirts of Cairo, the newspaper said.  Raya’s chief investment officer, Karim Hassan, wasn’t
available for comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ahmed A. Namatalla in Cairo at 
